MERN(React, Node.js, MonjoDB) Stack Application Setup Documentation

1. Installing MongoDB on ubuntu = https://www.mongodb.com/docs/manual/tutorial/install-mongodb-on-ubuntu/

2. Install Node.js and npm on Ubuntu = https://linuxize.com/post/how-to-install-node-js-on-ubuntu-20-04/ 

3. Downloading node.js application 
    # git clone https://github.com/Mrunal00712/nodejs-app-mern.git    //make changes in mongoC.js file for database
    # cd /n...
      /# npm install
       # npm start
       # curl http://localhost:4001

4. Downloading react application (front-end)
    # git clone https://github.com/Mrunal00712/reactjs-app-mern.git
    # cd /r...
      /# npm install
      /# npm start
       # curl http://localhost:3000

